INSERT INTO tap_horizon_receipts (
                signer_address,
                signature,
                collection_id,
                payer,
                data_service,
                service_provider,
                timestamp_ns,
                nonce,
                value
            ) SELECT * FROM UNNEST(
                $1::CHAR(40)[],
                $2::BYTEA[],
                $3::CHAR(40)[],
                $4::CHAR(40)[],
                $5::CHAR(40)[],
                $6::CHAR(40)[],
                $7::NUMERIC(20)[],
                $8::NUMERIC(20)[],
                $9::NUMERIC(40)[]
            )
